data.description: Horse property in the county with over 2.5 acres! This is a must see property & is set up nicely with plenty of room for all your animals! 2 pastures, 10 coveredstalls, covered hay barn, 40' round pen partially covered & perimeter is completely fenced! Nicely manicured property with lots of grass and designed for thatcountry living setting we all love! 3 bdrm, 2 bath home is well cared for with many nice features such as tile flooring, split floorplan, lots of kitchen cabinets, newer AC & more! Call now!Brokered And Advertised By: Realty ExecutivesListing Agent: Billie Ward
